---
import type { ContactoEmergencia } from '../data/talleres';
import Icon from './Icon.astro';

interface Props {
  contactos: ContactoEmergencia[];
}

const { contactos } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="emergency-section" id="emergencias">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-badge emergency-badge"><Icon name="alert" size={13} /> Urgencias</div>
    <h2>Contactos de Emergencia</h2>
    <p>En caso de peligro, no dudes en llamar. Estos servicios están disponibles las 24 horas del día.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="emergency-grid">
    {contactos.map((contacto) => (
      <a href={`tel:${contacto.numero}`} class="emergency-card" title={`Llamar a ${contacto.nombre}`}>
        <div class="card-glow"></div>
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <span class="contact-icon"><Icon name={contacto.icon} size={28} /></span>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <h3 class="contact-name">{contacto.nombre}</h3>
          <p class="contact-desc">{contacto.descripcion}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-number">{contacto.numero}</div>
        <div class="call-btn">
          <span>Llamar ahora</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>

  <div class="emergency-note">
    <span><Icon name="info" size={18} /></span>
    <p>Al hacer clic en cualquier tarjeta, tu celular iniciará la llamada automáticamente. En situaciones de peligro inmediato, llama al <strong>123</strong> (Policía).</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .emergency-section {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    scroll-margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .emergency-badge {
    background: #fef2f2;
    color: #dc2626;
    border: 1px solid #fecaca;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-header p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 15px;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .emergency-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .emergency-card {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #991b1b);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
  }

  .emergency-card:nth-child(even) {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b91c1c, #7f1d1d);
  }

  .emergency-card:nth-child(3n) {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c2410c, #9a3412);
  }

  .emergency-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.01);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.35);
  }

  .card-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -40px;
    right: -40px;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .icon-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .contact-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
  }

  .contact-info {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .contact-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: white;
  }

  .contact-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .contact-number {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  .call-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .emergency-card:hover .call-btn {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  }

  .arrow {
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .emergency-card:hover .arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  /* Note */
  .emergency-note {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    background: #fef2f2;
    border: 1px solid #fecaca;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    color: #7f1d1d;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .emergency-note span:first-child {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .emergency-note strong {
    color: #dc2626;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .emergency-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
